  "In November 2019, she agreed to sell 51% of her Kylie Cosmetics to beauty giant Coty Inc. for $600 million.",
  "The deal, which closed in January 2020, leaves Kylie in charge of creative efforts and marketing.",
  "She still owns 49% of the business, which she and her mother Kris Jenner grew through shrewd self-promotion and super low overhead costs.",
